opam-version: "2.0"
name: "obandit"
version: "0.2.1"
synopsis: "Ocaml Multi-Armed Bandits"
description: """
Obandit is an OCaml module for basic multi-armed bandits. It supports the
EXP3, UCB1 and Epsilon-greedy algorithms.

Obandit is distributed under the ISC license."""
